              Under this license you may not:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Modify or copy materials without authorization.</li>
              <li>Use materials for commercial public display.</li>
              <li>Attempt to decompile or reverse engineer platform software.</li>
              <li>Remove copyright or proprietary notices.</li>
              <li>Mirror materials on another server without permission.</li>
              <li>Violate the rights of others.</li>
              <li>Publish false or misleading information.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="h4 fw-bold mt-5 mb-3">3. Disclaimer</h2>
            <p>
              All materials are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, either expressed or implied.
